==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Aphakia
<hw>A*pha"ki*a</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.; Gr.
<grk>'a</grk> priv. + <?/ seed of a lentil.]</ety> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>An anomalous state of refraction caused by the absence of the
crystalline lens, as after operations for cataract. The remedy is the
use of powerful convex lenses.</def> <rj><au>Dunglison.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Aphakial</ent>⟦br⟧
